# AI Pipeline (6 stages)

1. Parser → 2. Scenarios → 3. Test Cases → **4. Test Data (local)** → **5. Skeleton (local)** → 6. Coverage

Stages 4–5 use `lib/test-data-builder.ts` and `lib/skeleton-builder.ts` — not Groq calls.

## Prompts

- One focused prompt per AI stage in `lib/prompts.ts`.
- Return **valid JSON only**; parse with try/catch and normalization in `lib/normalize-ai.ts`.
- Model: `llama-3.1-8b-instant` (free tier). See `lib/groq.ts`.

## Outputs

- Classify test case polarity via `classifyPolarity` / `sortAndFilterTestCases`.
- Sample outputs live in `samples/`; validate with `npm run test:validate`.

## Errors

Surface user-friendly messages in the dashboard; log server details without leaking API keys.
